#: ../../overview.rst:4
msgid "The device uses a small computer chip connected to your local WiFi network."
msgstr ""

#: ../../overview.rst:5
msgid "It regularly fetches the latest solar X-ray flux measurements from a NOAA GOES satellite"
msgstr ""

#: ../../overview.rst:6
msgid "The device interprets the data and uses a simple LED to display: - **No activity** → dim or steady light - **Low-level activity** → slow blink - **High activity** → fast blinking"
msgstr ""

#: ../../overview.rst:10
msgid "Configuration is done via a built-in WiFi setup portal, making it easy to connect the device to any home network."
msgstr ""

#: ../../overview.rst:12
